    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Mac OS X 常用命令]]></title>
    <link href="http://keleyundou.github.io/blog/2015/03/13/mac-os-x-chang-yong-ming-ling/"/>
    <updated>2015-03-13T11:46:11+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://keleyundou.github.io/blog/2015/03/13/mac-os-x-chang-yong-ming-ling</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>记录下平时在Mac终端常用的指令</p>

<p>当前工作目录</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>pwd</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>进入文件夹</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>cd 文件名</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>上级目录</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>cd ..</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>返回root</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>cd ~</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<!--more-->


<p>返回上一个访问的目录</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>cd -</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>删除</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rm -r 文件名</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>列出目录下所有文件</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>ls</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>将文件拷贝到目标目录下</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>cp 文件名 目标目录</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>新建文件夹</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>mkdir 文件夹名</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

]]></content>
